text: Hey @UPSHelp can I drop a "UPS Ground" Return box into a regular UPS box in my building? Or does it have to be special class? I got the return label from the company. So it's paid for.
@MsNycole Yes, you can drop the package off at the drop box that is at your building. The UPS driver will pick up the package at the scheduled time on the drop box. ^SB
@MsNycole You're welcome, have a good day! ^SB
